FIG. 1 is a rear perspective view of a snowmobile trunk bag having a collapsible beverage compartment in accordance with the invention;


FIG. 2 is a front perspective view of the snowmobile trunk bag shown in FIG. 1, with the collapsible beverage compartment fully deployed to allow storage of beverages; and


FIG. 3 is a front perspective view of the snowmobile trunk bag shown in FIGS. 1 and 2, with the collapsible beverage compartment compressed or collapsed to reduce the bulkiness of the trunk bag and to provide a better appearance when the collapsible beverage compartment is not being used for storing beverages.
